articles.author: Cheyenne MacDonald
articles.title: NASA will reveal what OSIRIS-REx brought back from asteroid Bennu on Wednesday - Yahoo News Australia
articles.description: NASA has a livestream planned for 11 AM ET on Wednesday, October 11 to reveal the sample its OSIRIS-REx spacecraft collected from asteroid Bennu.
articles.content:
NASA will give the public a look at the asteroid sample brought back to Earth by its OSIRIS-REx spacecraft next week. A livestream
